\/heavens-earth-praise-scholars\/","url_meta":{"origin":35416,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on &#8216;Ilm: Heaven and earth praise seekers of knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The\u00a0Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u00a0\"Whoever travels a path in search of knowledge, Allah will make him traverse a path to Paradise. Verily, the angels lower their wings in pleasure for the seeker of knowledge. The inhabitants of the heavens and earth, even\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38423,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/11\/01\/rahmah-khatam-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":35416,"position":5},"title":"Mujahid on Quran: Mercy descends upon finishing the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 1, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Hakam reported: Mujahid, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cMercy descends at the time of completing the entire Quran.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 30042 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0643\u064e\u0645\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u062c\u064e\u0627\u0647\u0650\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064f \u062a\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0632\u0650\u0644\u064f \u0639\u0650\u0646\u0652\u062f\u064e \u062e\u064e\u062a\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064f\u0631\u0652\u0622\u0646\u0650 30042 \u0645\u0635\u0646\u0641 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0634\u064a\u0628\u0629\u2026","rel":"","context":"In 